{"tid":1465573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解入機場？有咩目的？","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:09.000Z","uid":124932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"161b4da9f7269e7ff6b5c8101f3c98397cd51c16","tid":1465573,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解係去機場而唔係金鐘</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為機場有飛機、係癱瘓機場，取消班機=贏<br />\n<br />\n其實唔洗捨易取難走去挑狗機，挑贏都照飛<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5eRrdM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5eRrdM.jpg&h=ba149a19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上一來你唔會夠裝，二來機場冇路退<br />\n<br />\n機場係好牌，但唔係無敵<br />\n塞，阻，都唔會再比狗射盲眼，第一日冇人受傷冇人被捕，就證明方法正確<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好浪費呢張牌<br />\n唔係割蓆，除非你話狗咬人先，唔係既挑機前，<span style=\"color: gold;\">諗下點解係機場</span><br />\n<br />\n又除非你覺得比人拉左幾百人仲唔夠，唔係既話<br />\n<br />\n塞定阻都比唔上冇人比狗咬重要<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以回覆<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不被捕，不受傷</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和你飛，癱機場<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7777eb2d0e8d5e66052e9adacb4818c5a081c9d4","tid":1465573,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f271a74add4d0fcde6027f04629325d9864216","tid":1465573,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:23.000Z","msg":"入機場係智取"},{"pid":"52c4f79472c36b168c65040b74f04f9296c43780","tid":1465573,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"不宜力敵"},{"pid":"61d7580ac566909f8dd5de0532fa282d19a00267","tid":1465573,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:21:58.000Z","msg":"班機取消=贏"},{"pid":"983cb9497814662b755792fd93366206587e47fb","tid":1465573,"uid":124932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"不被捕，不受傷<br />\n和你飛，癱機場"}]}